\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7819457 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 I mean ordinary people, you may say about a person oh she's a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5271276 MI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7819457 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 Why do you think they were referred to as this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5271276 MI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8659632\charrsid15489505 Well they spoke nicely and very correctly and - they dressed just nicely but not loud. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7819457 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 Do you ever remember seeing a policeman when you were a child near w
here you were and did your mother ever frighten you by saying, if you're not good I'll tell a policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5271276 MI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 
Oh yes. Oh well - yes, perhaps she did as we grew older but when we were young we never saw a policeman because we were never out much you know only together. When we were on Moston Lane I don't think we had any policemen much up there.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7819457 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 How do you think the policemen treated the people though?
