\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7819457 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 Your mother came from Manchester?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5271276 MI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 Yes.
