\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5271276 MI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 No, not after they were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12347939 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
