 you would be bathed Saturday as well. And sometimes in the week, you know, - she might say, oh well, your - your hair wants washing, or something, you - you get dirty with being children, she'd say, the best thing to do is get in the bath.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7819457 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 Where did you bath - in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5271276 MI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7819457 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 How often did you put clean clothes on?
