m in the kitchen room because it wasn't a back kitchen, it was, you know, the sink wasn't in the room. Now we had our breakfast there because pa'd have gone out to work as they had to be at the office for half past seven or eight o'clock those days. Well 
we'd have our breakfast in that room and off to school. Well at night time, we'd have to have our tea in there and off to bed before pa came in.
