\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7819457 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 On Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5271276 MI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 Yes. And if you spoke at the table it was wrong. No, you weren't allowed to talk at the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7819457 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 Could you leave when you wanted?
