\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5271276 MI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15356496\charrsid15489505 Yes, when we brought somebody in and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8455755\charrsid15489505 then}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
